dc_title_s: Higo kokusei saikenzu: tsuketari ryakushi; Kashihara Yoshinaga seizu.
dc_description_s: Copperplate print. Oriented with north to the left. Relief shown pictorially. Inset: Kumamoto no zu, 1:18,000. Includes distance chart, list of population and number of households, area geography, etc. Engraved by Ōju. 1 map: col.; 47 x 66 cm., folded to 17 x 10 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
